    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Tony van Roon-Werten</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b3/Werten_37.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Werten_37.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tony van Roon-Werten <a href=\"/DOCCC_2004\" title=\"DOCCC 2004\">DOCCC 2004</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Tony van Roon-Werten</b>,<br />\na Dutch computer scientist, application manager and chess programmer. Tony is author of the chess program <a href=\"/XiniX\" title=\"XiniX\">XiniX</a> and was member of the <i>Search and Games Group</i> of the <a href=\"/Maastricht_University\" title=\"Maastricht University\">Maastricht University</a>. The development of XiniX started in the mid 90, soon supported by tester and operator <a href=\"/Elke_van_Roon\" title=\"Elke van Roon\">Elke van Roon</a>. \n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tony_van_Roon-Werten&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery17.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"PriAud76.jpg\" src=\"/images/3/32/PriAud76.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"332\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/ICT_2002\" title=\"ICT 2002\">ICT 2002</a>: <a href=\"/Bas_Hamstra\" title=\"Bas Hamstra\">Bas Hamstra</a>, <a href=\"/Sander_de_Zoete\" title=\"Sander de Zoete\">Sander de Zoete</a>, Tony van Roon-Werten (<a href=\"/XiniX\" title=\"XiniX\">XiniX</a>: 6th!), <a href=\"/Elke_van_Roon\" title=\"Elke van Roon\">Elke van Roon</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tony_van_Roon-Werten&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/0ee98f2a5c0ace0a\">Re: Stand alone Chess computers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony Werten</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">r.g.c.c</a>, April 10, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=119042\">Delphi / Winboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony Werten</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 13, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=262916\">0x88 revisited</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony Werten</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 01, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=276303\">Evaluation in REBEL (hanging pieces)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony Werten</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Hanging_Piece\" title=\"Hanging Piece\">Hanging Piece</a>, <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=312449\">Winboard problem (maybe Delphi only )</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony Werten</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 22, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=49450\">Adjusting weights the Deep Blue way</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tony van Roon-Werten</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 29, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a>, <a href=\"/Deep_Blue\" title=\"Deep Blue\">Deep Blue</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tony_van_Roon-Werten&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tony-van-roon-werten-302724131/\">Tony van Roon-Werten | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=127\">Tony van Roon-Werten's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tony_van_Roon-Werten&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery21.html\">24th Open Dutch Computer Chess Championship 2004 - Photo Gallery</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery17.html\">2nd International CSVN Tournament 2002</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301084911\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 47/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 102/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4029-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301084911 and revision id 7979\n -->\n"
